</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/michelle-johnson" hreflang="en">Michelle Johnson</a>
</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/culture/vow-trials-within-trials-yahia-lababidi" hreflang="und"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/blog/culture/labidivow.jpg?itok=iisbY-6b" width="250" height="175" alt="A silhouette of a woman&#039;s head turned in profile. Words are overlaid subtly across the tile." typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/culture/vow-trials-within-trials-yahia-lababidi"><em>The Vow:</em> Trials within Trials</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/yahia-lababidi" hreflang="en">Yahia Lababidi</a>
</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/culture/victory-our-revolution-final-triumph-tahirih-homa-darabi-and-blue-girl-shokoofeh-azar" hreflang="und"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/blog/culture/azarmural-w.jpg?itok=y_EzQFfn" width="250" height="175" alt="A mural of a woman&#039;s face with a pair of scissors near her head rendered in dark red. Text reads: Woman. Life. Freedom. " typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/culture/victory-our-revolution-final-triumph-tahirih-homa-darabi-and-blue-girl-shokoofeh-azar">The Victory of Our Revolution Is the Final Triumph of Tahirih, Homa Darabi…</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/shokoofeh-azar" hreflang="en">Shokoofeh Azar</a>
</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/culture/prey-behind-scenes-cinematic-comanches-dustin-tahmahkera" hreflang="und"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/blog/culture/tahmahkerafog-w.jpg?itok=EKsyPz1N" width="250" height="175" alt="A photographic still image of a young woman clothed in historical Comanche garb, brandishing a notched arrow as a large figure rises behind her in the fog" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/culture/prey-behind-scenes-cinematic-comanches-dustin-tahmahkera"><em>Prey:</em> Behind the Scenes with Cinematic Comanches</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/dustin-tahmahkera" hreflang="en">Dustin Tahmahkera</a>
</span></div>
        </li>
          </ul>
  </div>
